{
  "stem": "3928.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I seen them quite a bit, you know, what a misuse of people occurred you know, during this time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was going on until [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 19-- the end of 1943.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the end-- and in 1943, I had a meeting with a man, who-- my contact man, who took me over to a man by the name of Mr.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Schweikert.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, I hope I spell his name properly, S-C-H-W-E-I-K-E-R-T.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know his first name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He lived in Rakoczy Strasse in Budapest, Rakoczy utca.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Rakoczy is spelled R-A-K-O-C-Z-Y in-- in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't remember the address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's when they decided they need someone to get more information, what necessary to them, in order to be more active and more successful what they do in a resistance.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I spoke German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were able to attain a paper of-- by the name of George Nemeth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was about my height, my age.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they gave me this paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he says, you a Volksdeutsche right now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We want you, if you agree, to join the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was-- wasn't thinking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This was so romantic at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When you're a young man, everything is romantic to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I told him, fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I joined the Waffen SS under his name, under George Nemeth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then name was of-- the SS brigade was named SS Jagdverband-- Jagdverband Suedost Einsatzgruppe Ungarn.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was the name of the group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we went through all kind of a test.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, ma'am.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
